352
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:20,430
I guess it's time for me to leave here.

353
00:34:20,430 --> 00:34:24,950
It's nothing compared to CEO Han Young Won.

354
00:34:24,950 --> 00:34:28,350
Then, what's going to happen to us now?

