396
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:07,110
How about you?

397
00:37:07,110 --> 00:37:11,300
That's why. I'll be in touch.

398
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:13,850
Or why don't you take Han Young Won?

399
00:37:13,850 --> 00:37:18,850
