428
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:44,160
<i>It's okay. Give it to me.</i>

429
00:40:45,190 --> 00:40:51,850
<i>♫ I can't believe it, they say it's love ♫</i>

430
00:40:52,510 --> 00:40:59,130
<i>♫ What do I do? What do I do? What do I do? ♫</i>

431
00:40:59,130 --> 00:41:05,920
