432
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:12,890
<i>♫ What do I do with you? What do I do? ♫</i>

433
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:20,920
<i>♫ The more I hate you, the more you fill me up ♫</i>

434
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:24,770
<i>♫ I'm so afraid, I'm going crazy ♫
- Is there a law that says that a criminal's son has turn out like that?</i>

435
00:41:24,770 --> 00:41:30,890
<i>♫ The sun fully shines all over ♫
