00:41:47,300 --> 00:41:54,240
<i>♫ I love you, I love you, I love you ♫</i>

439
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:11,290
You can go.

440
00:42:19,270 --> 00:42:21,320
Chairman Han Tae Oh.

